    "title": "Narrating History: Sequence",
    "explanation": "Napoléon a trouvé Gustave. Le pétrole a disparu. Ensuite, tout a changé. — notice ensuite (then, next). It orders events in time.\n\nMultiple passé composé verbs in sequence tell a story: a trouvé, a disparu, a changé. Each one is a completed event.\n\nRe-read and put the events in order. What happened first? What happened ensuite?"
